    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and ready for its next big adventure! It runs like a dream and has been a joy to own. Whether you're planning a road trip or just need a solid daily driver, this car is ready to go. Come on by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
